 Ali ništa na zemlji ne može biti

492
00:20:35,380 --> 00:20:36,340
 dugo skladno.

493
00:20:36,340 --> 00:20:36,860
 Zašto?

494
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:38,440
 Zato što imamo lopova

495
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:40,040
 i ako mi nismo budni,

496
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:41,480
 ako mi ne čuvamo

497
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:42,360
 naše temelje,

498
00:20:42,360 --> 00:20:43,140
 naše biće,

499
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:43,860
 naše srce,

500
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:44,780
 našu dušu,

501
00:20:45,140 --> 00:20:47,100
 evo ti njega on prokopava.

502
00:20:47,100 --> 00:20:48,180
 I evo,

503
00:20:48,180 --> 00:20:50,420
 zato je važno,

504
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:51,940
 kaže Ivan Pavao II,

505
00:20:51,940 --> 00:20:54,620
 volio je govoriti o nedjelji.

506
00:20:56,860 --> 00:21:00,140
 Brinite se da se svijet ne ohladi,

507
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:01,240
 kaže Papa.

508
00:21:01,240 --> 00:21:04,800
 Pazite da se ne smrznete

509
00:21:04,800 --> 00:21:07,940
 u sebičnosti i konkurentskoj borbi,

510
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:11,500
 u praznom hodu zaposlenosti

511
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:13,120
 i lova za užicima.

512
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:16,040
 Pričite u uskrsnoj vatri

513
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:16,940
 sve te mise

514
00:21:16,940 --> 00:21:19,760
 i ne dajte da se iskvari nedjelja.

515
00:21:19,760 --> 00:21:21,680
 Dan, gospodnji.

516
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:24,380
 Dane u tjednu možemo zamisliti

517
00:21:24,380 --> 00:21:26,240
 kao vagone željeznice,

518
00:21:26,840 --> 00:21:29,060
 a nedjelju kao lokomotivu

519
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:31,380
 koja pokreće sve vagone

520
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:32,860
 sve dane u tjednu.

521
00:21:32,860 --> 00:21:35,660
 Evo, volio bih,

522
00:21:35,660 --> 00:21:37,520
 znam da se u ovoj zajednici moli,

523
00:21:37,520 --> 00:21:39,280
 volio bih da molimo

524
00:21:39,280 --> 00:21:41,100
 za neradnu nedjelju

525
00:21:41,100 --> 00:21:42,220
 u našoj domovini.

526
00:21:42,220 --> 00:21:44,600
 Imamo slobodnu domovinu

527
00:21:44,600 --> 00:21:46,320
 i lijepu domovinu,

528
00:21:46,320 --> 00:21:47,480
 a s druge strane

529
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:49,380
 osjećamo da postoji

530
00:21:49,380 --> 00:21:50,360
 jedno robstvo

531
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:52,420
 koje kao da nas želi uspavati

532
00:21:52,420 --> 00:21:54,740
 na način da su ljudi nezadovoljni.

533
00:21:55,120 --> 00:21:57,460
 jer kažu, pa moram i nedjeljom raditi,

534
00:21:57,460 --> 00:21:58,560
 pa onda nisam doma,

535
00:21:58,560 --> 00:22:00,340
 i onda neke stvari,

536
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:01,840
 neke špage pucaju.

537
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:04,700
 Evo, moramo moliti

538
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:06,480
 da vršimo Božje zapovjedi,

539
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:09,340
 jer Božje zapovjedi nisu naše zapovjedi.

540
00:22:10,120 --> 00:22:13,440
 Ili imam još malo vremena?

541
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,880
 Ima još vremena?

542
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:18,140
 Vidite,

543
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:20,280
 koji je put

544
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:21,880
 da bismo mi živjeli

545
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,300
 Božje zapovjedi?

546
00:22:23,300 --> 00:22:26,600
 Biti online,

547
00:22:26,600 --> 00:22:29,760
 biti povezan s Isusom Kristom.

548
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:31,960
 Koja je najjača veza

549
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:34,900
 naše povezanosti s Isusom?

550
00:22:34,900 --> 00:22:39,300
 Sveta misa.

551
00:22:39,300 --> 00:22:42,480
 Ja mislim, i sad izmislio ove neke signale,

552
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:43,520
 tek u zadnje vrijeme.

553
00:22:43,520 --> 00:22:45,300
 Ali sveta misa

554
00:22:45,300 --> 00:22:48,240
 je najsnažniji signal

555
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,700
 između nas i Boga,

556
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:50,460
 zato što nam

557
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:52,580
 po njoj sam Bog dolazi,

558
00:22:52,580 --> 00:22:54,220
 sam Isus dolazi

559
00:22:54,220 --> 00:22:55,040
 među nas.

560
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:57,300
 I sveta misa,

561
00:22:57,300 --> 00:23:00,840
 kada ulazimo srcem u svetu misu,

562
00:23:00,840 --> 00:23:02,100
 sveta misa nas budi,

563
00:23:02,100 --> 00:23:03,200
 budi našu vjeru.

564
00:23:03,200 --> 00:23:04,520
 Kada svećenik moli,

565
00:23:04,520 --> 00:23:07,200
 blagosvensi gospodine Bože svega svijeta,

566
00:23:07,200 --> 00:23:09,520
 tada ti u kalež,

567
00:23:09,520 --> 00:23:10,980
 u onaj kruh,

568
00:23:10,980 --> 00:23:13,300
 trebaš staviti svoje molitve.

569
00:23:13,300 --> 00:23:14,980
 Evo Isuse, donosim ti to.

570
00:23:14,980 --> 00:23:16,600
 Donosim ti svoje brige,

571
00:23:16,600 --> 00:23:17,620
 svoje roditelje,

572
00:23:17,620 --> 00:23:19,700
 onaj neuspjeh u školi,

573
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:20,920
 što sam se zbrukao,

574
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,580
 što mi nije ispalo ovo ili ono.

575
00:23:22,580 --> 00:23:24,120
 I stavljam to.

576
00:23:24,120 --> 00:23:25,580
 I kada, vidite,

577
00:23:25,780 --> 00:23:26,840
 svećenik moli

578
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:29,280
 po Hristu i s Hristom i u Hristu,

579
00:23:29,280 --> 00:23:30,560
 tada Bog Otac

580
00:23:30,560 --> 00:23:32,280
 vidi

581
00:23:32,280 --> 00:23:36,100
 tvoju molitvu u krvi i tijelu svoga Sina.

582
00:23:36,100 --> 00:23:37,600
 Ne može ne vidjeti,

583
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:38,840
 zato što je Isus

584
00:23:38,840 --> 00:23:41,020
 skupo za nas platio,

585
00:23:41,020 --> 00:23:42,760
 da bi nas u nebo doveo.

586
00:23:42,760 --> 00:23:45,000
 I zato trebamo biti budni.

587
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,680
 I zato nas do šaše,

588
00:23:46,680 --> 00:23:47,700
 potiče,

589
00:23:47,700 --> 00:23:49,080
 da budemo budni.

590
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:50,580
 I na kraju

591
00:23:50,580 --> 00:23:54,140
 tijel bih podijeliti s vama

592
00:23:54,140 --> 00:23:55,600
 kako biti budan

593
00:23:55,600 --> 00:23:56,700
 ovih dana,

594
00:23:56,700 --> 00:23:59,400
 jako nas je dobro potaknuo Papa Franjo,

595
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:03,140
 koji je 1.12. bio u Greću.

596
00:24:03,140 --> 00:24:05,260
 Tamo je svetište Jaslica.

597
00:24:05,260 --> 00:24:08,460
 I napisao je jedno pismo tog dana,

598
00:24:08,460 --> 00:24:09,980
 odnosno objavio pismo,

599
00:24:09,980 --> 00:24:12,320
 Admirabile signum.

600
00:24:12,860 --> 00:24:15,380
 To znači čudesni znak.

601
00:24:15,380 --> 00:24:17,880
 Čudesni znak Jaslica.

602
00:24:17,880 --> 00:24:19,440
 Papa Franjo piše,

603
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:24,260
 Jaslice su poput živog evanđelja,

604
00:24:24,260 --> 00:24:27,920
 koje izobilno teče sa stranica svetog pisma.

605
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:31,100
 Bog nas toliko ljubi,

606
00:24:31,100 --> 00:24:33,360
 da je postao jedno s nama,

607
00:24:33,360 --> 00:24:34,920
 kako bismo i mi

608
00:24:34,920 --> 00:24:37,240
 postali jedno s njime.

609
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:40,740
 Porijeklo Jaslica nalazimo

610
00:24:40,740 --> 00:24:41,560
 prije svega

611
00:24:41,560 --> 00:24:43,160
 u pojedinim detaljima

612
00:24:43,160 --> 00:24:44,720
 iz Isusova rođenja

613
00:24:44,720 --> 00:24:45,720
 u Betlehemu.

614
00:24:47,100 --> 00:24:48,900
 Došavši na ovaj svijet,

615
00:24:48,900 --> 00:24:51,540
 Boži sin pronalazi mjesto

616
00:24:51,540 --> 00:24:53,880
 gdje se hrane životinje.

617
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:55,800
 Sveti Augustin će reći

618
00:24:55,800 --> 00:25:00,420
 zašto je Marija položila Isusa u Jasle.

619
00:25:00,420 --> 00:25:02,660
 Jer nije imala kinderbed,

620
00:25:02,660 --> 00:25:04,100
 nije imala neko drugo mjesto,

621
00:25:04,100 --> 00:25:05,240
 nego Jasle.

622
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:06,820
 A što su Jasle?

623
00:25:06,820 --> 00:25:09,220
 Mjesto gdje se stavlja hrana.

624
00:25:09,220 --> 00:25:12,220
 I vidite, već u rođenju je prikazano

625
00:25:12,220 --> 00:25:14,760
 da će Isus biti naša hrana

626
00:25:14,760 --> 00:25:16,400
 u svetoj misi.

627
00:25:17,100 --> 00:25:19,340
 Papa nadalje nastavlja,

628
00:25:19,340 --> 00:25:22,160
 evo samo neki dijelovi iz pisma,

629
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:24,280
 kako je sveti Franjo

630
00:25:24,280 --> 00:25:26,660
 1223. godine

631
00:25:26,660 --> 00:25:28,520
 se vraćao od pape.

632
00:25:28,520 --> 00:25:32,120
 I prolazeći kroz to mjesto

633
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:34,100
 Greča,

634
00:25:34,100 --> 00:25:37,740
 vidio je da je krajolik

635
00:25:37,740 --> 00:25:39,140
 vrlo sličan Betlehemu,

636
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:41,860
 gdje on malo prije toga hodočastio.

637
00:25:41,860 --> 00:25:44,680
 I kada je Franjo to vidio,

638
00:25:46,340 --> 00:25:47,580
 u jednom trenutku je susreo

639
00:25:47,580 --> 00:25:48,980
 jednog žitelja toga mjesta,

640
00:25:48,980 --> 00:25:50,060
 zvao se Ivan,

641
00:25:50,060 --> 00:25:52,660
 i zamolio ga da mu pomogne.

642
00:25:52,660 --> 00:25:54,280
 Franjo je rekao Ivanu,

643
00:25:54,280 --> 00:25:57,460
 želio bih obnoviti uspomenu

644
00:25:57,460 --> 00:25:58,480
 na ono dijete

645
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:00,760
 koje je rođeno u Betlehemu

646
00:26:00,760 --> 00:26:03,440
 i na njegove djetinje potrebe

647
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,080
 i neprilike,

648
00:26:04,080 --> 00:26:04,580
 to jest,

649
00:26:04,580 --> 00:26:06,400
 kako je bilo smješteno

650
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:07,920
 u jaslice i položeno

651
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:10,060
 na slamu u nazočnosti

652
00:26:10,060 --> 00:26:11,420
 vola i magarca.

653
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:14,220
 tek što je to čuo,

654
00:26:14,220 --> 00:26:16,440
 njegov je vjerni prijatelj

655
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:17,140
 odmah

656
00:26:17,140 --> 00:26:19,140
 na naznačenom mjestu

657
00:26:19,140 --> 00:26:20,460
 otišao pripremiti

658
00:26:20,460 --> 00:26:23,040
 sve što je svetac poželio.

659
00:26:23,040 --> 00:26:25,640
 Dana 25. prosinca,

660
00:26:25,640 --> 00:26:26,640
 dakle na Božić,

661
00:26:26,640 --> 00:26:29,200
 1223. godine,

662
00:26:29,200 --> 00:26:30,660
 u Grečo su došla

663
00:26:30,660 --> 00:26:31,460
 mnoga braća

664
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:32,640
 iz raznih krajeva,

665
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:33,720
 a zajedno s njima

666
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:34,840
 i muškarci i žene

667
00:26:34,840 --> 00:26:36,620
 iz ubogih kućica

668
00:26:36,620 --> 00:26:37,440
 toga kraja,

669
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:38,720
 koji su donijeli

670
00:26:38,720 --> 00:26:40,340
 cvijeće i zublje

671
00:26:40,340 --> 00:26:42,120
 koje su rasvjetljivale

672
00:26:42,120 --> 00:26:43,760
 tu svetu noć.

673
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:45,660
 Kad je došao,

674
00:26:45,660 --> 00:26:47,280
 Franjo je našao jasle

675
00:26:47,280 --> 00:26:48,100
 sa sjenom

676
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:49,200
 vola i magarca.

677
00:26:49,200 --> 00:26:50,560
 Pred prizorom

678
00:26:50,560 --> 00:26:51,660
 Isusova rođenja

679
00:26:51,660 --> 00:26:52,740
 svi su prisutni

680
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:53,480
 doživjeli

681
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:56,240
 novu i neizreciu radost,

682
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:57,840
 koju nikad ranije

683
00:26:57,840 --> 00:26:59,000
 nisu iskusili.

684
00:26:59,000 --> 00:27:01,140
 Svećenik je zatim

685
00:27:01,140 --> 00:27:02,300
 svećano slavio

686
00:27:02,300 --> 00:27:03,500
 Euharistiju

687
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:04,440
 na jaslama,

688
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:06,180
 pokazujući vezu

689
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:07,600
 između utjelovljenja

690
00:27:07,600 --> 00:27:08,460
 Sina Božjega

691
00:27:08,460 --> 00:27:09,840
 i Euharistije.

692
00:27:09,840 --> 00:27:11,380
 U toj prigodi

693
00:27:11,380 --> 00:27:12,080
 u Greću

694
00:27:12,080 --> 00:27:13,240
 nije bilo kipova.

695
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:15,380
 Jaslice su realizirali

696
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:16,060
 i oživjeli

697
00:27:16,060 --> 00:27:17,500
 svi prisutni.

698
00:27:17,500 --> 00:27:21,040
 Naslada dalje Papa.

699
00:27:21,040 --> 00:27:22,100
 Zašto jaslice

700
00:27:22,100 --> 00:27:24,220
 nas drže

701
00:27:24,220 --> 00:27:25,660
 budnima?

702
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:27,100
 Jer nas potiču

703
00:27:27,100 --> 00:27:28,000
 da razmišljamo

704
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:29,000
 o tajstvu.

705
00:27:29,000 --> 00:27:30,840
 Zašto jaslice

706
00:27:30,840 --> 00:27:31,500
 pobuđuju

707
00:27:31,500 --> 00:27:32,720
 takvo čuđenje

708
00:27:32,720 --> 00:27:33,880
 i izazivaju

709
00:27:33,880 --> 00:27:35,000
 takvoga nuće

710
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:35,640
 u srcu?

711
00:27:36,180 --> 00:27:37,020
 Ponajprije

712
00:27:37,020 --> 00:27:38,340
 zato što

713
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:39,680
 očituju Božju

714
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:40,920
 nježnu ljubav.

715
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:43,900
 Postavljanje jaslica

716
00:27:43,900 --> 00:27:45,080
 u našim domovima

717
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:46,400
 pomaža nam

718
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:47,680
 ponovno oživjeti

719
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,740
 povijest onoga

720
00:27:48,740 --> 00:27:50,260
 što se zbilo

721
00:27:50,260 --> 00:27:51,460
 u Betlehemu.

722
00:27:58,460 --> 00:28:01,300
 Jaslice šalju jasnu poruku

723
00:28:01,300 --> 00:28:03,000
 da se ne smijemo

724
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:03,980
 dati zavarati

725
00:28:03,980 --> 00:28:04,900
 bogatstvom

726
00:28:04,900 --> 00:28:06,360
 i mnogobrojnim

727
00:28:06,360 --> 00:28:07,540
 ponudama

728
00:28:07,540 --> 00:28:08,360
 površne

729
00:28:08,360 --> 00:28:09,220
 i časovite

730
00:28:09,220 --> 00:28:09,940
 sreće.

731
00:28:09,940 --> 00:28:12,720
 Uspoređuje Papa

732
00:28:12,720 --> 00:28:13,360
 i kaže

733
00:28:13,360 --> 00:28:14,920
 zamislite kako je bilo

734
00:28:14,920 --> 00:28:15,640
 kod jaslica

735
00:28:15,640 --> 00:28:16,840
 kada se Isus rodio.

736
00:28:16,840 --> 00:28:18,300
 a kaže Papa

737
00:28:18,300 --> 00:28:19,340
 Herodova je

738
00:28:19,340 --> 00:28:20,720
 palača u pozadini

739
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:21,860
 zatvorena

740
00:28:21,860 --> 00:28:22,780
 gluha

741
00:28:22,780 --> 00:28:24,620
 za navještaj radosti.

742
00:28:24,620 --> 00:28:27,460
 Malo pomalo

743
00:28:27,460 --> 00:28:28,580
 nastavlja

744
00:28:28,580 --> 00:28:29,180
 stigli smo

745
00:28:29,180 --> 00:28:29,860
 do špilje

746
00:28:29,860 --> 00:28:30,680
 gdje se nalaze

747
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:31,380
 likovi

748
00:28:31,380 --> 00:28:32,620
 Marije i Josipa.

749
00:28:32,620 --> 00:28:33,960
 Marije je

750
00:28:33,960 --> 00:28:34,480
 majka

751
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:35,840
 koja promatra

752
00:28:35,840 --> 00:28:36,800
 svoje djetešce

753
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:37,700
 i pokazuje ga

754
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:38,120
 onima

755
00:28:38,120 --> 00:28:39,360
 koji ga dolaze

756
00:28:39,360 --> 00:28:40,180
 posjetiti.

757
00:28:41,200 --> 00:28:42,520
 Vidimo majku Božju

758
00:28:42,520 --> 00:28:44,060
 koja svog sina

759
00:28:44,060 --> 00:28:44,600
 ne drži

760
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:45,600
